language: East Sumbanese, Umbu Ratu Nggai dialect
Kadazan Dusun of Taginambur, Kota Belud, Sabah, Malaysia

annotation: could be makeua; 'v' would be irregular, but if make, then regular reflex
Possibly no primary colour term 'green' in POc.
Also means uncooked (eg. of meat, water), still soft (of cement); unripe; green (eg. of leaves)
